1️2️ Process Management
Check running processes
#top Or #htop

Kill process
#kill PID

Force kill
#kill -9 PID
________________________________________
1️3️ File Transfer Using PSCP
Upload file
#pscp file.txt user@192.168.1.10:/home/user/

Download file
#pscp user@192.168.1.10:/home/user/file.txt .
________________________________________
1️4️ Generate SSH Keys (PuTTYgen)
Open PuTTYgen
Steps: Click Generate
Move mouse randomly
Save: Private Key (.ppk)
Public Key
Add public key to server:
~/.ssh/authorized_keys
________________________________________
1️5 Exit Server
#exit or logout
